---
// Emergency Service Banner
---

<div class="bg-red-600 text-white py-2 px-4 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-red-700 opacity-50 animate-pulse"></div>
  <div class="relative z-10 flex items-center justify-center space-x-4">
    <span class="animate-pulse">
      <svg class="h-5 w-5 inline-block" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7 4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-9a1 1 0 00-1 1v4a1 1 0 102 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
      </svg>
    </span>
    <span class="font-semibold text-sm md:text-base">
      24/7 EMERGENCY SERVICE - Water in Your Basement? Call Now!
    </span>
    <a href="tel:4375450067" class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 bg-white text-red-600 px-3 py-1 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-amber-50 transition-colors">
      <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
      </svg>
      <span>(437) 545-0067</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>